<MethodEndpoint
  method={"get"}
  path={"/regions/{region}/intersections/{intersection_id}/cycle-times"}
  context={"endpoint"}
>
  
</MethodEndpoint>



This resource allows you to view the estimated cycle time time series of a single Intersection in a particular region.

Use `since` and `until` parameters to control the time range.
You can select time range of maximum 30 days.

You must set `since` and `until` to be a time in the past or present.
